JONES
v.
CLEVELAND CLINIC FOUND 2019-0390 Supreme Court of Ohio. June 26, 2019

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

APPEALS ACCEPTED FOR REVIEW Appeal accepted on proposition of law Nos. I and II. Kennedy, J., would also accept the appeal on proposition of law No. III.
